{
  "id": "63c10157f4ffe5001d6aab08",
  "title": "巻き肩",
  "created": 1673593182,
  "updated": 1701271986,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c10157f4ffe5001d6aab08",
      "text": "巻き肩",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593182,
      "updated": 1673593182
    },
    {
      "id": "6567377baff09e0000382ce1",
      "text": "鎖骨に指を這わせて外にスライドして、途中で止まるなら巻き肩",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701263228,
      "updated": 1701263255
    },
    {
      "id": "6567377baff09e0000382ce2",
      "text": "　伝わる？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701263228,
      "updated": 1701271986
    },
    {
      "id": "6567377baff09e0000382ce3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1701263228,
      "updated": 1701263228
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1015faff09e0000f577fb",
      "text": ">巻き肩と猫背の違いは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593184,
      "updated": 1673593209
    },
    {
      "id": "63c10179aff09e0000f577fd",
      "text": "> よく一緒だと思われがちな二つですが、巻き肩は肩が胸よりも前方に出るように歪んだ姿勢を指し、[猫背]は背骨が曲がり背中全体が丸くなった状態を指す。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593209,
      "updated": 1673593218
    },
    {
      "id": "63c10178aff09e0000f577fc",
      "text": "https://www.womenshealthmag.com/jp/fitness/a38395750/kaatsu-20211208/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593209,
      "updated": 1673593271
    },
    {
      "id": "63c102a0aff09e0000f5781c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593505,
      "updated": 1673593505
    },
    {
      "id": "63c101b7aff09e0000f577ff",
      "text": ">【巻き肩】",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593272,
      "updated": 1673593289
    },
    {
      "id": "63c101c8aff09e0000f57800",
      "text": "> 肩が丸まった状態になります。身体の横のラインが丸まっています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593289,
      "updated": 1673593289
    },
    {
      "id": "63c101c8aff09e0000f57801",
      "text": "> 背中は関係がないので、背筋は伸びているのに肩だけ内側に入り込んでいる方も多いです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593289,
      "updated": 1673593289
    },
    {
      "id": "63c101b7aff09e0000f577fe",
      "text": "https://www.ai-medical.co.jp/store/ai-media/health/7822",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593271,
      "updated": 1673593295
    },
    {
      "id": "63c102a2aff09e0000f5781d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593507,
      "updated": 1673593507
    },
    {
      "id": "63c101cfaff09e0000f57802",
      "text": ">巻き肩になると、首から肩、上半身の筋肉が縮んだままとなり、柔軟性を失います。すると血流が悪くなり、[肩こり]や[首こり]の原因となります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593295,
      "updated": 1701270486
    },
    {
      "id": "63c10223aff09e0000f57805",
      "text": "> また、巻き肩を改善しようと、無理して背筋を伸ばすと、腰が反った状態になりがちです。いわゆる「[反り腰]」になるので、背骨の本来のS字カーブが崩れて腰に負担がかかり、腰痛になるおそれがあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593379,
      "updated": 1673593411
    },
    {
      "id": "63c10223aff09e0000f57803",
      "text": "https://kumanomi-seikotu.com/blog/2924/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593379,
      "updated": 1673593406
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1023eaff09e0000f57806",
      "text": "\t>・[深呼吸]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593406,
      "updated": 1673594061
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57808",
      "text": "  > 1.両手を頭の後ろで組んで、両肘を外側に広げながら深呼吸します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593501
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f5780a",
      "text": "  > 2.巻き肩になった姿勢を伸ばしながら、酸素を身体いっぱいに取り込むイメージをしましょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593501
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f5780c",
      "text": " > ・[肩すぼめ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1701270471
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f5780e",
      "text": "  > 1.両肩を思いっきり上にあげ、脱力してストンと降ろします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593499
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57810",
      "text": "  > 2.次に左右の[肩甲骨]をギューっと寄せ、一気に力を抜きます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673594067
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57812",
      "text": "  > 3.これを各3回ほど行いましょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593499
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57814",
      "text": " > ・[肩回し]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1701270467
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57816",
      "text": "  > 1.両手を肩に添え、両肘を大きな円を描くように回します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593497
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57818",
      "text": "  > 2.目線は上に、反り腰にならないようにします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593497
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f5781a",
      "text": "  > 3.内回し、外回しを10回ずつ行いましょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593484,
      "updated": 1673593497
    },
    {
      "id": "63c1028baff09e0000f57807",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673593483,
      "updated": 1673593483
    }
  ]
}